title: Skillfeed Game Development with Python
description:
Skillfeed Game Development with Python


Join game developer Kevin O'Flaherty for this course with hours
of video lecture, dozens of code samples and lab exercises
designed to help you remember everything! Take this course only
if you want to learn professional game development techniques
This course is taught in Python. You'll be learning how to
develop games, and the concepts this course covers can then be
applied to any programming language
